All Known Implementing Classes:
PlaylistCellController
Enclosing class:
PlaylistCellView
public static interface PlaylistCellView.PlaylistCellViewListener
Listener interface for handling events or retrieving data for the PlaylistCellView. Implement this interface to provide the necessary library information for the cell view.
